            "body": "nice. should we update `vim_na_files.txt` and/or [scripts/vim-patch.sh](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/03f746e913904ea8291d13ac7236f65a8c1eec26/scripts/vim-patch.sh#L194) ? or is that a bad idea since we might need to \"merge\" upstream changes to the Makefile? @zeertzjq @janlazo ",
